content:
[[module css]]
#header {
    background-image: url(https://files.scpfoundation.net/local--files/theme:russian-art-hub/scp-art-hub.png);
}

@media (min-width: 768px) {
#header {
    background-size: 90px;
}
}

#header h2 span {
    color: transparent;
    text-shadow: none;
}

#header h2 span::before {
    content: 'SCP-RU艺作中心';
    color: #f0f0c0;
    text-shadow: 1px 1px 1px #000000;
    text-shadow: 1px 1px 1px rgba(0,0,0,.8);
}

[[/module]]
[[iftags +版式]]
在你的作品开头添加如下语法以应用此版式：
> @@[[include theme:russian-art-hub]]@@
[[/iftags]]
